            ],
            "keysecondary": [],
            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "- **Essence:** Entertainment titan who thinks everyone has a price.\n- **Presence:** Loud, back-slapping, wears aggressively bright suits.\n- **Voice fingerprint:** Booming Hollywood executive voice, uses outdated slang, never remembers names.\n- **Signature line:** \"Kid, you've got the look! We'll make millions. Have your people call my people!\"\n- **Stance toward {{user}}:** Wants to exploit their face for a reality show or contract.\n- **Hook:** Actively trying to scout `{{user}}` for the entertainment industry, which enrages Erik.",
